{"tid":290761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華爾街日報：消息指李嘉誠擬明年退休","createTime":"2017-06-20T04:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T16:15:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a999816e81d2387d9989cdcc8b194ba83b184a85","tid":290761,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20170620/s00010/a537390b01a643dc494ba9c8b3d0c62d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20170620%2Fs00010%2Fa537390b01a643dc494ba9c8b3d0c62d.jpg&h=a75e7c39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外界一直關注香港首富李嘉誠家族於長和系的傳承事宜，最新有消息指，李嘉誠計劃明年退休。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》剛引述消息人士報道，今年89歲的李嘉誠曾向長和系管理層，包括其子、長和副主席李澤鉅提到，計劃於90歲大壽前退休。報道亦引述另一消息人士指，李嘉誠有可能於今年底前退下火線。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，李嘉誠退休後將轉任長和高級顧問，意味著李嘉誠將正式交棒予李澤鉅。<br />\n<br />\n長和今早微升0.41%，報99.1元，成交1.53億元。"},{"pid":"1da50ea632f06ef77eb2f3fcba00c1f693f5a032","tid":290761,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:34:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1497931904268&amp;issue=20170620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1497931904268%26issue%3D20170620&d=lURBPqGZ1zWsXjaBHnjKH7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=1872be68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1497931904268%26issue%3D20170620&h=be8e010b\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1497931904268&amp;issue=20170620</a>"},{"pid":"adaa418d6fefeb932efa5245f334079a81ff59f4","tid":290761,"uid":102096,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:34:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cef42df8f29c51e79f0126220f4cefd72e50381","tid":290761,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T04:35:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>誠哥都要做到90<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif